name: Zip Compressed GraphML File
summary: Learn about .GRAPHMLZ files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Since GRAPHMLZ files use Zip formatting, you can decompress them back to a standard GRAPHML file using a Zip decompression utility such as 7-Zip or WinZip.

description: GraphML file (.GRAPHML) compressed with .ZIP compression; contains a graph comprised of nodes and edges as well as their properties; used for reducing the file size of standard GraphML files for sharing and storage.
